Comment: 10,0:19:24.05,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got it!
Comment: 10,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a piece of cake!
Comment: 10,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!{## should be correct, coming from a servant}
Comment: 10,0:19:30.05,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Andrew! I didn't expect you to be a pro at piano.
Comment: 10,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am. I'm perfect. {BITCH, please}{## not liking "natural" for touzen here, as you might have noticed}
Comment: 10,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike someone as slovenly as yourself.
Comment: 10,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess the spell wore off.
Comment: 10,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Comment: 10,0:19:58.02,0:19:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Comment: 10,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here. There are\Nno good girls around anyway.
Comment: 10,0:20:03.35,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I should've known. Of course this would happen.
Comment: 10,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte.
Comment: 10,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think those clothes suit you a lot better. {my fucking man}
Comment: 10,0:20:18.32,0:20:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Frank. When's the next time you have off?
Comment: 10,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to visit the library?
Comment: 10,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is there anywhere else you'd like to go?
Comment: 10,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you mean together?
Comment: 10,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the feeling we'd get along well.{## cute pairing}
Comment: 10,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it possible to be so beautiful?
Comment: 10,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's return home.
Comment: 10,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte Jansson.
Comment: 10,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's homely at first glance.
Comment: 10,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I saw her sad smile, and I realized...
Comment: 10,0:21:01.96,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the sort of kindhearted girl\Nyou rarely find nowadays. {if only there were multiple, but alas}
Comment: 10,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you and Atsuko Kagari?
Comment: 10,0:21:08.47,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Comment: 10,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you didn't kick her out.
Comment: 10,0:21:12.53,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignored an order from your witch-hating father.
Comment: 10,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is a brilliant statesman.
Comment: 10,0:21:20.20,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that does not mean our opinions will always align.
Comment: 10,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Comment: 10,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl has caught your interest.
Comment: 10,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:21:35.30,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lotte! Frank asked you out, but you refused?!
Comment: 10,0:21:38.96,0:21:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm happy he did, but I felt it'd be rude to go on a date with him before I developed any feelings.
Comment: 10,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him we should start as friends.
Comment: 10,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, I bet you think you don't need a \Nboyfriend as long as you have {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}. {/s/boyfriend/girlfriend s/nightfall/anime}{## yeah...}
Comment: 10,0:21:54.91,0:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. So Akko, how about you? {how do we manage to miss each other on these so often}
Comment: 10,0:21:58.07,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it make you happy to have a prince put the moves on you?
Comment: 10,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only because the bee stung him!
Comment: 10,0:22:04.63,0:22:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it put you on cloud nine.
Comment: 10,0:22:06.41,0:22:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Profess your love, with lips so fine.\NYou've lit my fire, you must be mine."
Comment: 10,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There might come a day when Andrew says "I love you" for real.
Comment: 10,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! That selfish, conceited guy would never say that!
Comment: 10,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd tell him?
Comment: 10,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no! Never, ever!
Comment: 10,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously never! Even if I died!
Comment: 10,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Comment: 10,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}It'll never happen!
